On the other hand, if we think it s more than funny or weird that these two events i.e., Malusi and the dagga occurred within the same temporal window, if we ascribe to them a meaning beyond the merely coincidental , we have entered the realm of the synchronous. the Natal Indian Immigrants Commission Report of 1887): Meaning, the criminalisation of dagga in South Africa was hitched from the start to the white man s need to control, subdue and demonise his non-white brother. DM DM